21: // The resource_names field in DiscoveryRequest specifies a route configuration.
22: // This allows an Envoy configuration with multiple HTTP listeners (and
23: // associated HTTP connection manager filters) to use different route
24: // configurations. Each listener will bind its HTTP connection manager filter to
25: // a route table via this identifier.
26: service RouteDiscoveryService {
